File: Neuenschwander-2025-EG-239.pgn

GBR: +0100.03a8c7 FEN: K7/2k2ppp/8/8/8/8/8/3R4 w - - 0 1

1. Ka7 f6! The most tenacious defence. (1… Kc6 2. Kb8 f5 3. Kc8 f4 4. Kd8 f3 5. Ke7 +- (5. Rf1? Kd5 6. Rxf3 Ke4 7. Rf7 g5 8. Rxh7 g4 =) ) (1… f5 2. Rd5 g6 3. Rc5+ Kd6 4. Kb6 f4 5. Kb5 +-) 2. Ka6 Kc6 (2… g5 3. Kb5 +-) 3. Ka5 Kc5 4. Ka4 (4. Rd7? g5 5. Ka4 Kc4 6. Ka3 Kc3 7. Ka2 Kc2 8. Rxh7 g4 9. Rg7 f5 =) 4… Kc4 5. Ka3 (5. Rd7? g5 6. Ka3 Kc3 etc., see 4. Rd7 ) 5… Kc3 6. Ka2 Kc2 7. Rb1! (7. Rh1? g5 8. Rxh7 g4 9. Rg7 f5 =) 7… g5 (7… f5 8. Rb2+ Kd3 9. Kb1 g5 transposes to the main line ) 8. Rb2+ Kd3 9. Kb1 g4 10. Kc1 f5 11. Kd1 1-0.
